data.description: Stunning two-year-old open concept home located in Brightwood neighborhood. This three bedroom two and a half bath home built by AJ Construction is bright and open with 9' ceilings, shiplap wall, fireplace, and first floor primary bedroom for true easy living.Gorgeous upgraded kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances, gas range with airfry oven, granite countertops and a beautifully polished glass mosaic backsplash. The downstairs primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a spacious walk-in closet and elegant crown molding. Ensuite has a wonderful frameless glass door enclosing the upgraded tiled shower wall and floor.Beautiful oak stairs lead to two bedrooms each with walk-in closets. Upstairs second full bathroom boasts dual sinks and a tastefully appointed tile floor.  Outdoor living is a delight, with a large front porch, rear covered porch, and 10x10 slab with gazebo, perfect for dining and entertaining. The Gullah blue rear side fences offer both privacy and a picturesque open forest view in the backyard. Home is complete with a one-car detached garage with epoxy floors.  This wonderful community offers a fantastic neighborhood pool, perfect for cooling off on hot summer days. This is a great opportunity to live in new home and enjoy modern, comfortable living in a thriving community conveniently located to everything the Lowcountry has to offer.
